These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, software-developer, freelancer
1. the software-developer is on the far left##1
2. the firefighter is on the right of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | software-developer | freelancer | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, electrician, videographer
1. the videographer is on the far right##1
2. the social-worker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | social-worker | electrician | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, dancing, photography
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | chess | dancing | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
