.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, train
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | train | jet-ski | tram |

