.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | comedy | documentary |

